<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Sebald I. Pfinzing, Bürger und Ratsherr zu Nürnberg</head><p>Der Rat weist an, die Herausgabe der zu Bozen beschlagnahmten Waren Nürnberger Bürger und Kaufleute zu erwirken und Neuigkeiten mitzuteilen.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_153" id="76v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_153_r1l1"><expan>Sebolt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>pfıncʒ<ex>ing</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> lıeber <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> vnd <expan>Ratgeſell<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_153_r1l2"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Sebolt vns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etwıeuıl <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> kawffleẅt auf heẅt fürbracht daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_153_r1l3">Jn <expan>bottſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> ſey daʒ ſıe ein michle hab ʒu Bocʒen vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> enden </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_153_r1l4">in dem gebırg <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . dıe Jn <expan>ernid<ex>er</ex>gelegt</expan> ſey vnd noch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>heft</expan> mug </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_153_r1l5"><expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> . Alſo ıſt <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> . Ob ſıch dıe ſache <expan>ʒwıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>gnedıgſt<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_153_r1l6"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ dem <expan>Römıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> künıg . vnd dem <expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> von <expan>Öſterr<ex>eich</ex></expan> <expan>yend<ex>er</ex>t</expan> ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_153_r1l7"><expan>frıd<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>rıchtıgu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> <expan>mache<ex>n</ex></expan> wölt . <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> ob vns von des dıenſts <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_153_r1l8">ein ſchub möcht <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> als du von vns gefertıgt bıſt . daʒ du denn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_153_r1l9">von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> vnd kawffleẅt hab <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> . das beſt fürkereſt damıt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_153_r1l10">Jn ır hab <expan>volg<ex>en</ex></expan> möcht . vnd daʒ das niht <expan>v<ex>er</ex>geſſen</expan> oder <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſawmt</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_153_r1l11">wurd . vnd doch das darauf Jn geheim haltſt ſo du beſt mugeſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_153_r1l12">als du wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſteeſt</expan> daʒ des ein notdurft ıſt / Vnd was dır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_153_r1l13">lewff vnd mer begegnen . das ſchreıb vns allweg <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>cʒogenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_153_r1l14"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> georij </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_153" id="76v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Sebolt<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Pfincz<ex>ing,</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> lieber <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und
                                <expan>ratgesell<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Sebolt, uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        etwievil <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> kawfflewt auf hewt fürbracht, daz in
                                <expan>bottsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> sey, daz sie ein
                        michle
                        hab zu Boczen und <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> enden in dem gebirg
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, die in
                            <expan>ernid<ex>er</ex>gelegt</expan> sey und noch
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>heft</expan> mug <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>. Also
                        ist <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>, ob sich die sache
                            <expan>zwisch<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedigst<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren,</expan> dem <expan>römisch<ex>en</ex></expan> künig,
                        und dem <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan> von
                            <expan>Österr<ex>eich</ex></expan>
<expan>yend<ex>er</ex>t</expan> zu <expan>frid<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> zu <expan>richtigu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>mache<ex>n</ex></expan> wölt <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> ob uns von
                        des diensts <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> ein schub möcht
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, als du von uns gefertigt bist, daz
                        du denn von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und kawfflewt hab
                            <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> das best fürkerest, damit in ir hab
                                <expan>volg<ex>en</ex></expan> möcht und daz das niht
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>gessen</expan> oder
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>sawmt</expan> wurd, und doch das darauf in geheim
                        haltst, so du best mugest, als du wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>steest</expan>, daz
                        des ein notdurft ist; und was dir lewff und mer begegnen, das schreib uns
                        allweg <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czogenl<ex>ich</ex></expan>.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Georii. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
